1. *Snova* sam sanjao da letim na mesečini. (I dreamt of flying on the moon.)

2. Živeo sam skromno u svojim *snovama*. (I lived modestly in my dreams.)

3. Nije ostvario svoje *snove*. (He didn't fulfill his dreams.)

4. Uvek sam verovao u svoje *snove*. (I always believed in my dreams.)

5. Ona je težila da ispuni svoje *snove*. (She strived to fulfill her dreams.)

6. On je bio zarobljen u svojim *snovima*. (He was trapped in his dreams.)

7. Ovo je ono o čemu sam *snovao*. (This is what I dreamed of.)